<inglise>Amendment of earlier legislation </inglise>
<eesti>Rahvatervise seaduse (RT I 1995, 57, 978; 1996, 3, 56; 49, 953; 1997, 37/38, 569; 1999, 30, 415; 88, 804; 2001, 23, 128): </eesti>
<inglise>The Public Health Act (RT I 1995, 57, 978; 1996, 3, 56; 49, 953; 1997, 37/38, 569; 1999, 30, 415; 88, 804; 2001, 23, 128) is amended as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>1) paragrahvi 4 punktist 5 j&auml;etakse v&auml;lja s&otilde;nad "ja kiirgusohtlike seadmete"; </eesti>
<inglise>1) in clause 4 5), the words "and equipment involving a radiation hazard" are omitted; </inglise>
<eesti>2) paragrahvi 12 l&otilde;ike 1 punktist 2 j&auml;etakse v&auml;lja s&otilde;nad "radionukliide sisaldavate ainete v&otilde;i seadmete,"; </eesti>
<inglise>2) in clause 12 (1) 2), the words "substances or equipment containing radionuclides" are omitted; </inglise>
